    Supports adjustable parameters see AdjustableParameter

      • getPreProcessors

        public final java.util.List<PreProcessingStrategy> getPreProcessors()
        Specify the preprocessors required for this detector.

        The individual strategies in the list can be produced using the generic methods PreProcessingStrategy.of(String, Class...) or PreProcessingStrategy.of(String, boolean, Class...) in the interface, or using a fully custom PreProcessingStrategy class.

        The string name of each of the strategies is used as the key reference in the preprocessed dataset given to the IDetector.buildWorkers(List) method
        Specified by:
        getPreProcessors in interface IDetector<T extends DetectorWorker>
        Returns:
        a list of the required preprocessing strategies
